          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zeus_quan/" class=" " title="肾上腺素">肾上腺素</a>
                (卖保险的牢骚篓子)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13733417">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">《追我魂魄》，纪实的语言竟能如此优美。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-07-15 16:19</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                《追我魂魄》，纪实的语言竟能如此优美。
